[{},{"attrs":{"title":"PostCSS plugins","description":"How to add PostCSS plugins?"},"body":"<h1><a id=\"how-to-add-postcss-plugins-\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#how-to-add-postcss-plugins-\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>How to add PostCSS plugins?</h1><h3><a id=\"recommended-method\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#recommended-method\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Recommended Method</h3><p>If present, rename or delete the <code>postcss.config.js</code> in your project directory. Then, in your <code>nuxt.config.js</code> file add the following:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">build</span>: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">postcss</span>: {\n      <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add plugin names as key and arguments as value</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Install them before as dependencies with npm or yarn</span>\n      plugins: {\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Disable a plugin by passing false as value </span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'postcss-url'</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'postcss-nested'</span>: {},\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'postcss-responsive-type'</span>: {},\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'postcss-hexrgba'</span>: {}\n      },\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">preset</span>: {\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Change the postcss-preset-env settings</span>\n        autoprefixer: {\n          <span class=\"hljs-attr\">grid</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre><h3><a id=\"legacy-method\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#legacy-method\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Legacy Method</h3><p>** Attention: This is deprecated **</p>\n<p>Use <code>postcss.config.js</code>, for example:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs \">const join = require('path').join\nconst tailwindJS = join(__dirname, 'tailwind.js')\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [require('tailwindcss')(tailwindJS), require('autoprefixer')]\n}</code></pre>","docLink":"https://github.com/nuxt/docs/blob/master/en/faq/postcss-plugins.md"}]